org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class Catalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.OnyxVector
      • org.onyxplatform.api.java.Catalog

  • public class Catalog
extends OnyxVector
    A catalog holds a set of tasks which can be passed to and run in a job. A catalog derives from an OnyxVector.
